{"tid":1899781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不招待支那客】光榮冰室老闆向平機會挑機：「告我種族歧視吧！」","createTime":"2020-02-26T22:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T03:00:33.000Z","uid":202464,"like":382,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a10c045cc57888b300bf8f584adcf987c6fc7525","tid":1899781,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:02:36.000Z","msg":"近日光榮冰室張貼告示，只招待香港人，平機會勸喻該店撤回，但強調沒有提及檢控。<br />\n<br />\n光榮老闆Glory受訪時下戰書，平機會放馬過來，「我很希望他告我，告我種族歧視吧，如果我一個人被罰錢，然後define到香港人與大陸人是兩個種族，我又覺得OK。」<br />\n<br />\nGlory期望平機會搬出《種族歧視條例》，告他一狀，「其實他很尷尬，他告我，便代表中國和香港是兩個種族；你不告我，簡單點說代表你自己多餘。」只要成就大業，一己受罰算甚麼，「如果罰錢可以separate香港與大陸，我又覺得不錯，相信很多人會來支持這件事，我想大部份香港人都會。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平機會回覆本報查詢，表示不評論個別個案，並重申早前論點，指有關職員依照既定程序，過程中沒有提及警告或控告光榮。"},{"pid":"9722ed7e97905dd878a4efbb4022681f5aa4e739","tid":1899781,"uid":70487,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:03:25.000Z","msg":"好串<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaccf51d59b6e71b6710529b300770cf9bb15782","tid":1899781,"uid":53466,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a70a90a6c8dafa6295ac81d9adde3a7a9bbd176e","tid":1899781,"uid":162724,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:12:03.000Z","msg":"齋問題-你哋覺得黃絲應該係點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2db2896bb789e365658b1b069bdc6bbaf4555a2","tid":1899781,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38d8f22ed8af7aa5463276834bd9a1263ce5bfc","tid":1899781,"uid":183601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T22:17:13.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid